Topic: Functions

Standard: Use a function multiple times in a song, such as repeating a chorus

Lesson: Functions - Explore

Skill Progression: Define & Call a function by refactoring existing code (ie: code exists; drag out function and update it, then call the function)

Pretest Modality: Given starting code / shadow blocks, refactor

Posttest Modality: Given algorithm / intent / incorrect code, match with code

